### Get all sessions
GET http://localhost:7190/api/sessions

### Create a new session
POST http://localhost:7190/api/sessions

### Get a specific session (replace {sessionId} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:7190/api/sessions/{sessionId}

### Get messages for a session (replace {sessionId} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:7190/api/sessions/{sessionId}/messages

### Add a message to a session (replace {sessionId} with actual ID)
POST http://localhost:7190/api/sessions/{sessionId}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Content": "Hello, this is a test message",
  "Role": "User"
}

### Delete a session (replace {sessionId} with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:7190/api/sessions/{sessionId}
